\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf6 <$Scr_Ps::4>Summary:}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 Evan's unexpected gift left Sarah speechless\hich\f2 \emdash \loch\f2 a plaque acknowledging her as the class valedictorian. She stepped onto the stage to accept it, the crowd's cheers filling the room. Then, urged by the spectators, she faced the audience to find Evan, down on one knee, offering a ring. Battling her inner turmoil, Sarah said yes, eliciting ecstatic cheers from the crowd, though her father's expression betrayed his unease.<!$Scr_Ps::4>}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch \f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7
\par\pard\plain \tx0\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf6 <$Scr_Ps::4>Leading Context:}
\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf7 The school year had ended, and Sarah had finished at the top of her class. This scene occurred the day after everyone had graduated. In the previous scene, Sarah discovered that Evan had invited her parents to their graduation party. She didn't know why, and during the conversation with her parents, she tried unconvincingly to persuade them, and perhaps herself, that her relationship with Evan was merely a senior year fling.<!$Scr_Ps::4>}
