\par\pard\plain \tx0\li346\fi14\sb60\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 Evan:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::3> Evan's excitement was at a maximum level. This was his moment. In front of Sarah's parents and nearly 40 of his friends and fellow graduates, Evan proposed to Sarah. <!$Scr_Cs::3>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 Sarah:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::3> Sarah's inner turmoil was at its peak once Evan proposed to her. While her mind flipped through ways that she could reject or postpone her answer to Evan's proposal, her heart and her lips accepted his proposal. Outwardly, Sarah looked like a happy, freshly engaged woman. But on the inside, she felt shame and guilt as she saw the look on her father's face when her parents exited the room after she accepted Evan's proposal. <!$Scr_Cs::3>}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf8 Sarah's parents: }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf1 <$Scr_Cs::3>Sarah's parents, especially her father, were upset and disappointed when Sarah accepted Evan's proposal.<!$Scr_Cs::3><!$Scr_Ps::5>}
