\par\plain {\f4\fs22\b0\i1\cf9 Evan had told Sarah's parents that her surprise would begin at exactly 30 minutes into the party. He welcomed them to stay if they wanted providing them comfortable chairs at the back of the room. He also told him that he would be happy to email them or text them if they wanted to go back to their room. Sarah's parents opted to sit in the chairs and wait for her surprise. ] }
